snippet: Jacintha Saldanha, who was tricked by a prank call to the hospital where Kate Middleton was staying, was found hanging and had left several notes, a preliminary inquest hearing was told on Thursday.
lead_paragraph: Jacintha Saldanha, who was tricked by a prank call to the hospital where Kate Middleton was staying, was found hanging and had left several notes, a preliminary inquest hearing was told on Thursday.
